<div class="wsd-page__content">
    <div class="wsd-welcome">
        <div class="wsd-welcome__hero">
            <img src="/assets/images/sysdig-inspect-logo-color-620x96.png">
        </div>
        <div class="wsd-welcome__body">
            <div class="wsd-welcome__card-list">
                <div class="wsd-welcome__card">
                    <div class="wsd-welcome__card-content">
                        <p>
                            As a very easy quick start, here's how to capture all of the system events on a Linux box with sysdig:
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <code>
                                sudo sysdig -w filename.scap
                            </code>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="wsd-welcome__card-footer">
                        <a href="https://github.com/draios/sysdig/wiki/Sysdig-User-Guide" class="sd-button sd-button--lg" target="_blank">sysdig user guide</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wsd-welcome__card" {{action "openFileBrowser"}}>
                    <div class="wsd-welcome__card-content">
                        Sysdig Inspect works with trace files that have been collcted by sysdig on a Linux system.
                    </div>
                    <div class="wsd-welcome__card-footer">
                        {{#if isElectron}}
                            {{#sd-button
                                iconName="file_black"
                                color="primary"
                                size="lg"
                                title="Open capture"
                                click=(route-action "openFileBrowser")
                            }}
                                Open Capture
                            {{/sd-button}}
                        {{else}}
                            {{sd-input
                                name="file-path"
                                placeholder="Capture file path"
                                isAcceptChangeMode=true
                                changeValue=(route-action "openFile")
                            }}
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="wsd-welcome__card">
                    <div class="wsd-welcome__card-content">
                        <p>
                            Need help?
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Join our <a href="https://slack.sysdig.com" target="_blank">public Slack channel</a> for announcements and discussions.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            For documentation, issues, suggestions, and contributions, please go to <a href="https://github.com/draios/sysdig-inspect" target="_blank">the project on Github</a>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
